{
  "stem": "25591.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because those early years, I mean, particularly during the war, I was, of course, hoping and praying and rooting and working to have the other side win.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And this became particularly poignant when I was in a forced labor camp north of Budapest, where the British and American Air Forces were bombing us all the time.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I had very mixed feelings because I wanted the-- the bombing raids to be very successful in that the railroad be destroyed, on which I was working.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But still, you were hoping that you might survive.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I-- I really was too busy with my day-to-day life to have, you know, long-term fears or concerns.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I-- I knew the times-- that the times will be difficult and they'd be particularly difficult for Jews.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I was.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I had personal experiences in-- with that and-- and let me tell you what they are.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's one of my most vivid memories.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] In what used to be North East Hungary, there is a fairly major town, the Czechoslovak name for it is Kosice.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Hungarian name is Kassa.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My younger-- my young uncle was a high school teacher and his high school was one of the high schools that went up to Kassa, Kosice, when the Hungarians took it over.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I went with them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I was part of this unbelievable, you know, German, Hungarian fascist invasion of democratic Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was an unwitting, unwilling participant, waving the Hungarian flag.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I remember when Mussolini's son-in-law, Count Ciano, the Italian foreign minister, came to Budapest.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And my school was one of the schools that lined the main street, [INAUDIBLE], which is a beautiful boulevard.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
